^ Agriculture at a Crossroads (c) 2009" (PDF). International Assessment of Agricultural Knowledge, Science and Technology for Development. [11 February 2016]. 
^ Stutz B. Wanted: GM Seeds for Study. Seed Magazine. 1 July 2010. （原始內容存檔於5 July 2010）. 


